---
import ContentLayout from '../layouts/ContentLayout.astro';
---

<ContentLayout
  title="Contact | YourWhiteScreen"
  description="Contact YourWhiteScreen for questions, suggestions, or feedback about our free online screen tools."
  lang="en"
  canonical="/contact"
>
  <style>
    h1 { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #111; }
    p { margin-bottom: 16px; color: #444; }
    .contact-box {
      background: #f7f7f7;
      border: 1px solid #e5e5e5;
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 28px;
      margin-top: 24px;
    }
    .contact-box p { margin: 0; }
    a { color: #0066cc; }
    h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 28px 0 8px; color: #222; }
    ul { margin: 0 0 14px 20px; color: #444; }
    ul li { margin-bottom: 6px; }
  </style>

  <h1>Contact Us</h1>
  <p>Have a question, suggestion, or bug report? We'd love to hear from you.</p>

  <div class="contact-box">
    <p>You can reach us by email: <a href="mailto:franruizlozano31@gmail.com">franruizlozano31@gmail.com</a></p>
  </div>

  <h2>Common questions</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Can I use the tools commercially?</strong> Yes, all tools are free for personal and commercial use.</li>
    <li><strong>The colors look different on my screen.</strong> Color accuracy depends on your display calibration. Our tools output exact CSS hex values but your monitor may render them differently.</li>
    <li><strong>Can I request a new tool?</strong> Absolutely — send us an email with your idea.</li>
    <li><strong>Is there an API?</strong> Not currently, but we're open to discussing integration options.</li>
  </ul>

  <p>We aim to reply within 48 hours.</p>
</ContentLayout>
